3) cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper proposes a novel unsupervised learning method for depth estimation. 
4) cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also possible as the paper uses a neural network for depth estimation. 
5) cs.MM (Multimedia) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper deals with video depth estimation.
